= preparation

The key is in setup.py and "pip install -e ."

cd ~/github.com/umatobi && \
    virtualenv umatobi && \
    cd umatobi && \
        source ./bin/activate && \
        cd .. && \
    pip3 install -e .

= play samples

$ python3 umatobi/theater.py --sample
$ python3 umatobi/theater.py --moving-squares

= There are various for starting test.

# see: https://realpython.com/python-testing/
$ python3 umatobi/tests/test_all.py
# __name__ means "__main__".
$ python3 umatobi/tests/test_unit.py
$ python3 umatobi/tests/test_integration.py

$ python3 -m unittest umatobi.tests.test_unit
# __name__ means "umatobi.tests.test_unit".
# "from umatobi.tests.unit.xxx import XXX" launch test suite.
$ python3 -m unittest umatobi.tests.test_integration
$ python3 -m unittest umatobi.tests.unit.test_lib
$ python3 -m unittest umatobi.tests.integration.test_client_with_watson

$ python3 -m unittest discover -s umatobi/tests
$ python3 -m unittest discover -t umatobi/tests -s unit
$ python3 -m unittest discover -t umatobi/tests -s integration

= enjoy development !

Edit some files.
